      body
        .container
          .row
            .span4.offset4
              img(src='img/logo.jpeg', alt="logo")
          .row
            ul.thumbnails
              li.span4
                a.thumbnail(data-toggle='modal', href='#app-factory-modal', role='button')
                  img(alt='App Factory Icon', src='img/app_factory.png')
                  h3 App Factory
              li.span4
                a.thumbnail(data-toggle='modal', href='#partytonight-modal', role='button')
                  img(alt='PartyTonight Icon', src='img/PartyTonight.png')
                  h3 PartyTonight
              li.span4
                a.thumbnail(data-toggle='modal', href='#whats-for-lunch-modal', role='button')
                  img(alt="What's For Lunch Icon", src='img/Whats_For_Lunch.png')
                  h3 Whats For Lunch?
          .row.offset1
            ul.thumbnails
              li.span4
                a.thumbnail(data-toggle='modal', href='#bs-generator-modal', role='button')
                  img(alt='BS Document Generator Icon', src='img/bs_generator.png')
                  h3 BS Document Generator
              li.span4
                a.thumbnail(data-toggle='modal', href='#matcher-modal', role='button')
                  img(alt='Matcher Icon', src='img/matcher.jpg')
                  h3 Matcher
        #app-factory-modal.modal.hide.fade.in(aria-hidden='true', aria-label='app-factory-label', role='dialog', tabindex='-1')
          .modal-header
            button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') &times;
            h3#app-factory-label App Factory
          .modal-body
            p App Factory allows you to easily convert your scripts into full applications.
            p
              | It works with any script you can run from the command line and allows using custom icons.
            a(href='https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/app-factory/id556464792?ls=1&mt=12', target='itunes_store')
              img(alt='App Factory - Immersive Applications', src='http://r.mzstatic.com/images/web/linkmaker/badge_appstore-lrg.gif', style='border: 0;')
            iframe.github(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=App-Factory&type=fork&size=large') Your browser does not support inline frames or is currently configured not to display inline frames. Content can be viewed at actual source page: http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=App-Factory&type=fork&size=large
          .modal-footer
            button.btn(data-dismiss='modal') Close
        #bs-generator-modal.modal.hide.fade.in(aria-hidden='true', aria-label='bs-generator-label', role='dialog', tabindex='-1')
          .modal-header
            button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') &times;
            h3#bs-generator-label BS Document Generator
          .modal-body
            p
              | The BS Document Generator takes all the difficulty out of creating your buzzword-compliant documentation. Impress your friends with your "synergistic visionary metrics" and easily generate PDF documentation for your next meeting.
            a(href='https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/bknoocfigoeaaoiffhdaigclkaeoencg')
              img(alt='BS Generator Chrome Store', src='img/chrome_badge.png')
            iframe.github(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=BS-Document-Generator&type=fork&size=large')  Your browser does not support inline frames or is currently configured not to display inline frames. Content can be viewed at actual source page: http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=BS-Document-Generator&type=fork&size=large
          .modal-footer
            button.btn(data-dismiss='modal') Close
        #matcher-modal.modal.hide.fade.in(aria-hidden='true', aria-label='matcher-label', role='dialog', tabindex='-1')
          .modal-header
            button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') &times;
            h3#matcher-label Matcher
          .modal-body
            p
              | Matcher uses your profile to scan your friends list and calculate the people most compatible with you.
            a(href='http://facebookmatcher.herokuapp.com/')
              img(alt='Matcher - Facebook App', height='100', src='img/Facebook-App-Center.jpeg', width='100')
