            button.btn(data-dismiss='modal') Close
        #partytonight-modal.modal.hide.fade.in(aria-hidden='true', aria-label='partytonight-label', role='dialog', tabindex='-1')
          .modal-header
            button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') &times;
            h3#partytonight-label PartyTonight
          .modal-body
            p
              | Looking for something to do? With PartyTonight finding a party is easy. This app allows you to find, rate, and share a fun time with everyone in your community. The days of being out of the loop are over. With this app you will always know whats going on in your town and with the rating system you will know the details of all parties around you.
            p
              | PartyTonight gives you the power to find the most interesting parties and avoid the lame ones. The days of sitting at home bored are over. The iPhones location service will show you exactly where the parties are taking place and how to get to them fast! All parties are not created equal, let PartyTonight be your tool to success when it comes to having fun in your town.
            a(href='http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/partytonight-ad-supported/id436667981?mt=8&uo=4', target='itunes_store')
              img(alt='PartyTonight - Ad Supported - Immersive Applications', src='http://r.mzstatic.com/images/web/linkmaker/badge_appstore-lrg.gif', style='border: 0;')
            iframe.github(src='http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=PartyTonight-iPhone-App&type=fork&size=large') http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=jakesjews&repo=PartyTonight-iPhone-App&type=fork&size=large
          .modal-footer
            button.btn(data-dismiss='modal') Close
        #whats-for-lunch-modal.modal.hide.fade.in(aria-hidden='true', aria-label='whats-for-lunch-label', role='dialog', tabindex='-1')
          .modal-header
            button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') &times;
